result.formatted_address: G/F, 134 Portland St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Northern Dumpling Yuan

reviews.text:
Panfried dumplings are definitely better than the boiled ones.
So juicy inside with crispy crust.
I also ordered the hot and sour soup to go with these dumplings.
We had leek and beef, cabbage and pork, so good!
Cheap local yummy food.
Must try if u want a taste of Chinese food:)
An old hand-made dumplings restaurant,  it also has shanghai noodle
One of the best dumplings place I had in the world. I almost come here every week. I wanna go there right now...

The dumplings are great, with heaps of fillings to choose from. Price is within reasonable range, too. The only thing I'm not satisfied with is that it was quite a long wait for food. Luckily I wasn't in a rush.
Yummy.  Reasonable price

result.adr_address: G/F, 134 Portland St, Mong Kok, 香港
result.formatted_address: G/F, 134 Portland St, Mong Kok, 香港
result.name: 北方餃子源

reviews.text: Worth trying. 圖中是煎韮菜豬肉餃，水京蔥羊肉餃，麻醬冷麵。

湯淡到好似清水咁，d麵又脹又淋
食左一粒餃子一啖麵就走左，咁既水準收四十蚊，食撚到躁
店員禮貌很好，食物又美味~ 上菜又快~

Panfried dumplings are definitely better than the boiled ones.
So juicy inside with crispy crust.
I also ordered the hot and sour soup to go with these dumplings.
We had leek and beef, cabbage and pork, so good!
Cheap local yummy food.
Must try if u want a taste of Chinese food:)
價錢比一般餃子店貴，但勝在足料，湯餃味道比較淡，煎餃皮脆加上豆瓣醬很好吃，比較推介👍🏻
